race.description: Nbn News Country Boosted Maiden Handicap
race.comment: MAURRAQA (1) debuts for a sharp barn and is a half by Maurice to a multiple Group 1 winner. Won the first of his two recent trials. Mallyon sticks aboard, and he draws inside. Profiles well and the betting will be key. STRATTON (4) just missed last time over 1250m at this track. Close to a win and he gets his chance here. FLEE WITH ME (2) resumes today after filling a minor placing at Grafton over 1725m. Has switched to the Samantha McGuren stable. May find this a touch short, but she rates strongly. Likely to be wound right up and should make her presence felt. JUNOSTAR (3) is a debut fitted with two Gold Coast trials. Has a soft gate and may be the best of the remainder.
